Package: mobspain
Title: Spanish Transport Zone Analysis
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Prince", "Oppong Boakye", email = "prynx44@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Author: Prince Oppong Boakye [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Prince Oppong Boakye <prynx44@gmail.com>
Description: A minimal R package for accessing Spanish administrative zones
    for transport analysis. Provides easy access to spatial zone geometries
    with filtering capabilities for cities, regions, and specific zones.
    Designed to work seamlessly with the comprehensive transport analysis
    demonstrated in the package vignette.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
